				<div class="window">
					<div id="how1" class="how-step active">
						<img src="assets/how/how1.png" alt="" />
						<p>Through ambassadors in the countries where we are currently present and promotion in university campuses, AddUp seeks outs students who are accepted or currently enrolled in university, but need a little extra money to complete their tuition costs. 					
						</p>
					</div>
					<div id="how2" class="how-step">
						<img src="assets/how/how2.png" alt="" />
						<p>After an application process to validate that the student is indeed accepted or enrolled at a university and has a current student ID, their signing an honor code pledging to fulfill the charitable rewards, and making sure that their profile meets AddUp’s requirements and standards, the student’s story and the charitable contributions he offers in return, go live for the duration of the campaign.</p>
					</div>
					<div id="how3" class="how-step">
						<img src="assets/how/how3.png" alt="" />
						<p>Students then use the free social media tools provided by AddUp’s platform to get relatives, friends, alumni or fellow nationals who share a common regard for the quality of a US education to contribute towards their tuition. </p>
					</div>
					<div id="how4" class="how-step">
						<img src="assets/how/how4.png" alt="" />
						<p>Simultaneously, AddUp’s ambassador’s promote AddUp with alumni of the student’s university and/or people from their country, thus expanding the student’s potential network of donors. </p>
					</div>
					<div id="how5" class="how-step">
						<img src="assets/how/how5.png" alt="" />
						<p>Through contributions starting from $1, anyone can be inspired by a student’s story and cause. Once inspired, it takes less than 3 minutes to add up to his education. Donors can further help a student by sharing his story on Facebook, Twitter or by e-mail. </p>
					</div>
					<div id="how6" class="how-step">
						<img src="assets/how/how6.png" alt="" />
						<p>At the end of the campaign, AddUp pays the collected money directly to the university towards the student’s tuition.</p>
					</div>
					<div id="how7" class="how-step">
						<img src="assets/how/how7.png" alt="" />
						<p>The student has the rest of the year to study without worrying about his finances...</p>
					</div>
					<div id="how8" class="how-step">
						<img src="assets/how/how8.png" alt="" />
						<p>…and to fulfill his promises of paying it forward through charitable contributions of creativity, energy and time. </p>
					</div>
					<div id="how9" class="how-step">
						<img src="assets/how/how9.png" alt="" />
						<p>By posting updates throughout the year, donors are kept informed of the students advances in this regard.</p>
					</div>

